reviewText: A very well made and informative documentary about the city of Abraham our beloved father of faith! You will learn and be enlightened!
Very interesting and enjoyed it.  Useful for group Bible studies.

A very good DVD explaining the conflict & the bible history of this incredible place. It is very well done. The only bad thing I have to say about it is that it is very short. I was surprised that it was over so quickly. However, for less then $10 it was worth it.
